content: RT @TeamTrumpAmanda Kiefer was assaulted in 2008 while walking to dinner in San Francisco by an illegal alien.He was released from prison thanks to the "Back on Track" program implemented by then District Attorney Kamala Harris.Our country would not be safe with Kamala in the White House.
